content: I'm having some trouble establishing a consistent wake-up routine. I was doing pretty well for a bit, but then I had a big project at work that threw everything off. I've been trying to get back on track, but it's been tough. By the way, I recently started taking a morning yoga class on Tuesdays and Thursdays, which has forced me to wake up at 6:45 AM on those days, and it's actually been really helpful.
